(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/transform\"><code>transform()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/translate\"><code>translate()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>Die <code><strong>CanvasRenderingContext2D.canvas</strong></code> Eigenschaft, Teil der <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API\">Canvas API</a>, ist eine Nurlese-Referenz auf das <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement</code></a> Objekt, das mit einem gegebenen Kontext assoziiert ist. Sie kann <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators/null\"><code>null</code></a> sein, wenn kein assoziiertes <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas\"><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code></a> Element existiert.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><var><em>ctx</em></var>.canvas;</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiele","title":"Beispiele","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Wenn dieses <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas\"><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code></a> Element gegeben ist:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>canvas</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>canvas<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>canvas</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p>... kannst du eine Referenz auf das Canvas-Element innerhalb von <code>CanvasRenderingContext2D</code> herstellen, indem du die <code>canvas</code> Eigenschaft verwendest.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> canvas <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'canvas'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> ctx <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> canvas<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getContext</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'2d'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>canvas <span class=\"token comment\">// HTMLCanvasElement</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Spezifikation</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/scripting.html#dom-context-2d-canvas\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'CanvasRenderingContext2D.canvas' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Lebender Standard</span></td>\n   <td></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser-Kompatibilität","id":"browser-kompatibilität","isH3":false,"query":"api.CanvasRenderingContext2D.canvas","dataURL":"/de/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/canvas/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"siehe_auch","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D</code></a> interface</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API\">Canvas API</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Beispiele","id":"beispiele"},{"text":"Spezifikationen","id":"spezifikationen"},{"text":"Browser-Kompatibilität","id":"browser-kompatibilität"},{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"siehe_auch"}],"summary":"Die CanvasRenderingContext2D.canvas Eigenschaft, Teil der Canvas API, ist eine Nurlese-Referenz auf das HTMLCanvasElement Objekt, das mit einem gegebenen Kontext assoziiert ist. Sie kann null sein, wenn kein assoziiertes <canvas> Element existiert.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"CanvasRenderingContext2D.canvas","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"CanvasRenderingContext2D.canvas","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"CanvasRenderingContext2D.canvas","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"CanvasRenderingContext2D.canvas","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"CanvasRenderingContext2D.canvas","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/canvasrenderingcontext2d/canvas","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/canvasrenderingcontext2d/canvas/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D","title"